* Q: How to upgrade from System 6 to System 7 if I 
don't _already_ have<BR>
System 7.0.1* boot disks?<BR>
<BR>
A: You can download System 7.0*, 
7.0.1* and 7.5.5 from Apple. However,<BR>
Apple sites now store these as .smi images 
that can't be opened in System 6<BR>
(or 7.0)! It was not a smart move from Apple to 
