possible, use another mac running System 7.0.1 and up to decode .smi<BR>
images to 
System 6-compatible Disk Copy 4.2 format (and write the disk<BR>
images back to 
floppies).<BR>
<BR>
If using a lone System 6 mac:<BR>
<BR>
2. Download System 7.0* or 7.0.1* from 
other sites that have them in Disk<BR>
Copy 4.2 format.<BR>
